{
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "这里有好多的东西，好多闪亮的石头啊。",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "哈哈！看来宝石也照不亮你的眼睛啊！来挑选一块吧！",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你看起来没什么想要的呢……那就随便看，反正我也不着急。",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "我这里有千万颗宝石，但好像没有一颗能让你停下脚步的……",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "那就听你的，让我随便选一块吧。\n[i][font_size=22]由乃随手拿起一块不起眼的石头。[/font_size][/i]",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "哈哈哈！你拿走了我这里最好的！",

  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "又醒了，还要重复吗……",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...去... 塔里... ..继续... 吧.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...你又来了... \n...明知道... 一切... ..都会重来.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...你.. 还需要... ..什么...？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "如果要给我什么……算了……你给不了我想要的。",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...去吧... \n..塔顶也好... 塔底也罢... ..反正... 还会见面.....[/sine]",

  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "华丽的房间，你好耀眼，我什么都没有……但什么也不需要……",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "哎呀呀，就算什么都没有，被我轻轻一照也会发光的哟。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你这种什么都不想要的性子倒是有趣，让我来给你打扮打扮吧。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "就算觉得没有想要的，也该让自己看起来体面一些呀。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "你肯定没有……不过随便你。\n[i][font_size=22]由乃站在原地，像一尊忘了上色的空心雕像。[/font_size][/i]",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "啧，真是个不懂风情的姑娘。拿去吧——这是我剩下最后一点热情了。",

  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你跳得好高，你想要为谁跳舞吗？",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "这里！！这里只有我一个人！毛茸茸！",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你想要什么？我这里有好多好东西！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "从其他世界来的？好好！那里有什么？",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "好多好多有趣的东西！小小人知道好多！",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "好！好！！这些是我送你的！",

  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你的鼾声很均匀。像这世上最后一件还有规律的事。",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你的心比我还安静……拿去吧，这是属于安静者的馈赠……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]不争不抢的人，往往走得最远……你是不是根本没打算走？[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]我的肉不会催促你……它只会陪着你发愣……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回答",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……痛也好，睡也好，醒也好。其实都差不多。\n[i][font_size=22]由乃的语气很轻，像在说一件与己无关的事。[/font_size][/i]",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]收下吧……让你继续坐在这里……看潮起潮落，却不必湿脚……[/thinky_dots]",

  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "你要战斗，我拒绝。",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "[b]不能！！拿着这把武器！去战斗！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "[b]你的血还是温的！既然活着，就挥一下让我看看！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "[b]你为什么而战？！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "你要打就打吧。\n[i][font_size=22]由乃把剑尖垂向地面，像把一场战斗随便搁在一边。[/font_size][/i]",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "[b]拿着，这把剑是你的战利品，你要往前走！别回头！[/b]",

  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "火很暖。但我没有什么需要捂热的东西。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "没有也能暖暖手呀。进来吧，让我在无聊中把你[jitter][b]焐热[/b][/jitter]一下。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你身上空荡荡的——是不是连[jitter][b]情绪[/b][/jitter]都打包寄走了呀？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "尝尝这个[jitter][b]点心[/b][/jitter]吧。不需要着急吃完的那种哦。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "……味道这种东西，有和没有差不多。但既然递过来了。\n[i][font_size=22]由乃接过去，只咬了一口。[/font_size][/i]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "真是个有趣的孩子。那就捧着吧——等它慢慢[jitter][b]凉[/b][/jitter]掉。",

  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.char": "恶魔也做交易。我的灵魂……你想要就拿去。",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1.ancient": "没怎么用过的[sine]灵魂[/sine]，反而最容易卖出高价呢……",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你连讨价还价的兴趣都没有？这种[sine]空荡荡[/sine]的态度——真让人着迷。",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "如果契约上只写一个字——[sine]\"无\"[/sine]——你签么？",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "回应",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "\"无\"是个好字。比我的名字还有分量。签吧。\n[i][font_size=22]她的签名轻得像没有墨水的笔，在纸上留下一道看不见的划痕。[/font_size][/i]",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "有趣！我从未见过有人把[sine]虚无[/sine]签得如此坚定。拿去——这是你的空白的代价。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0r.ancient": "你不属于这里？为什么要来见我？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-0r.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1r.char": "告诉我回家的方法。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.0-2r.ancient": "回家？不可能。我没有告诉你的理由。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.ancient": "你又回来了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-1r.char": "我必须让你吐出口。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.1-2r.ancient": "还不放弃吗？我的所为只是为了维持秩序。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0r.ancient": "塔记得你。你来了很多次，真顽强啊，还要进行多少次呢？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1r.char": "……",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.YUNO_MOD_CHARACTER_YUNO_CHARACTER.2-2r.ancient": "那就战吧。"
}